---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Home
seo:
  title: "Kati Sunray STUDIO - Thoughtful Gifts for Baby, Parents & Extended Family"
  description: "Cherishing simple (and precious) family moments & celebrating presence with our little ones through books, prints, cards, and keepsakes."
---

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="hero-gradient section-padding">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-serif font-semibold text-gradient mb-6 animate-fade-in">
        Thoughtful Gifts for Baby, Parents & Extended Family
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto animate-slide-up">
        Cherishing simple (and precious) family moments & celebrating presence with our little ones through books, prints, cards, and keepsakes.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-500 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto animate-slide-up">
        Mindful positive parenting, living and leading
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center animate-slide-up">
        <a href="{{ '/shop/' | url }}" class="btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4">
          Browse the Shop
        </a>
        <a href="{{ '/about/' | url }}" class="btn-secondary text-lg px-8 py-4">
          Our Story
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Featured Products Section -->
<section class="section-padding bg-white">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-semibold text-gradient mb-4">Featured Products</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Discover our carefully curated collection of meaningful gifts that celebrate the joy of family moments.
      </p>
    </div>
    {% set featuredProducts = collections.products | sortByData('home_feature_order') %}
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      {% for p in featuredProducts %}
        {% if loop.index0 < 3 %}
          <div class="animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: {{ loop.index0 * 0.1 }}s">
            {% productcard p %}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <a href="{{ '/shop/' | url }}" class="btn-primary">
        View All Products
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Where You Can Find Us Section -->
<section class="section-padding bg-gradient-to-br from-neutral-50 to-brand-50">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-semibold text-gradient">Where You Can Find Us</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3 text-neutral-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p>Available at <a class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700" href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Makers%20The%20Beaches%2C%201984%20Queen%20St%20E%2C%20Toronto%2C%20ON%20M4L%201J2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Makers The Beaches, 1984 Queen St E, Toronto, ON M4L 1J2</a></p>
        <p>Online/ecommerce direct orders by <a class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700" href="mailto:katisunray@gmail.com">email</a> and e-transfer (shipping cost extra).</p>
        <p>Baby book available at <a class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700" href="https://a.co/d/be3MDU6" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Amazon</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- About Preview Section -->
<section class="section-padding bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-50 to-accent-50">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-semibold text-gradient mb-6">
        Made with Love in Canada
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Each piece is thoughtfully created and printed in Ontario, designed to bring joy to families and create lasting memories. From baby books to art prints, every item tells a story of love, presence, and the beautiful chaos of family life.
      </p>
      <a href="{{ '/about/' | url }}" class="btn-secondary">
        Learn More About Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

